#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use the roles associated with the access token, which are checked by default"
msgstr "Utilize as funções associadas ao token de acesso, que são verificadas por padrão"

